&DEVC ID='D_0_2_RADM_HF', QUANTITY='NET HEAT FLUX', XYZ=0.075000,-0.150000,0.000000, IOR=-1 /
! ── 材料: 丙烯酸塑料 → 判据[equipment/风挡侧窗] 部件=风挡侧窗 T_crit=200℃ τ=45s ──
&DEVC ID='D_1_0_WINS_WT', QUANTITY='WALL TEMPERATURE', XYZ=1.775000,0.350000,1.150000, IOR=-1 /
&DEVC ID='D_1_0_WINS_HF', QUANTITY='NET HEAT FLUX', XYZ=1.775000,0.350000,1.150000, IOR=-1 /
